es and borders, athletes do not have the ability to appropriately prepare for these Games, and their health and safety must come first.\\\"\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current global restrictions\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"public gatherings\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"training facilities\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"borders\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"their health\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group also called on broadcasters, specifically NBC, and sponsors \\\"to adopt the same level of duty of care toward athletes by supporting the IOC and (International Paralympic Committee) with flexibility and understanding during these uncharted times.\\\"\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9924522114062961, \"rank\": 0.0073228034048372056, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.088594956359944e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q